{"tid":1103753,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛賓沮喪：或沒法再替拜仁披甲","createTime":"2019-04-12T15:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T15:54:27.000Z","uid":199590,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ddb65a1a9b31cf52b412ad74720e5ed70d910e9","tid":1103753,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】荷蘭老將洛賓坦言，可能在離隊前也不能再為拜仁慕尼黑上陣。<br />\n<br />\n35歲的洛賓（Arjen Robben）於周四接受天空體育訪問時，對復出顯得悲觀：「我有我的關注，我不肯定能否在本季再為拜仁慕尼黑作賽。不清楚問題所在令人感到困擾。」<br />\n<br />\n本季將會是洛賓加入拜仁慕尼黑後的第10個和最後一個球季。然而，他今年受傷很嚴重，在所有比賽中只有15次上陣。這位荷蘭球員因大腿和小腿傷患，自去年11月尾歐聯大勝賓菲加5:1後，便未曾再為一隊上陣，他較早前坦言自己最希望在離隊前，再一次為拜仁披甲。<br />\n<br />\n過去10年，洛賓為拜仁贏過7次德甲及4次德國盃，並在2013年歐聯決賽對多蒙特攻入致勝的一球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688c34733c972bab2ffa60ebaa75b51c8460f5ae","tid":1103753,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"洛一式將成歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade8ea439927fd9cc8e47abee460bdc385d56d44","tid":1103753,"uid":120965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"賓賓可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f912fc2b1b379374b252940ce875a118638220d","tid":1103753,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"人總會老<br />\n無辦法<br />\n<br />\n條撚樣, 世紀單刀唔入, 攪到荷蘭無冠"}]}